Job 4 : Planning Analysis
Task 1 : Calculate :
a. No. of Voters to get added in next X years
Hive solution: select count(*) from census where age+3 > 18;
b. No. of Senior Citizen to get added in next X years
Hive solution: select count(*) from census where age+3 > 65;
c. Sex Ratio
Hive Solution: select gender, count(*) from census group by gender;
d. Citizen vs. Immigrants Ratio for all Employed
Hive Solution: select weeksworked, citizenship, count(*) from census where citizenship like '%Native%' or citizenship like '%naturalization%' group by weeksworked, citizenship;
